frames.caption: A giant, knitted white rabbit stands towering between two rows of buildings, casting a shadow over the street. A person stands in the foreground, gazing up at the enormous figure, creating a surreal juxtaposition of scale. The sky is clear with a few clouds, adding to the whimsical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal urban setting where a massive, knitted rabbit figure is positioned between tall buildings. The presence of a person looking up at the rabbit emphasizes the fantastical scale and adds a sense of wonder.

The scene is bathed in soft, warm light, enhancing the dreamlike quality of the setting.
